name: DARKNESS
description:
Hello Darkness, my old friend.

Each person has a side that hides dark secrets. Trying to hide the outside face and the insider would walk freely in the dark areas! Any entrance would be forbidden except for your real one. But one day each of us (the smart ones or the simple ones) will open up our dark side to the right person. Let’s be hopeful that RIGHT person won’t say a word to anyone and won’t use our darkness.
